327
00:26:50,410 --> 00:26:53,200
But it provided the Zhang Family
with great significance.

328
00:26:54,580 --> 00:26:56,880
The Zanghai Flower
is within the Bronze Door.

329
00:26:57,930 --> 00:27:01,339
