331
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:05,550
Only the head of the Zhang Family

332
00:27:05,820 --> 00:27:07,200
can enter the place.

333
00:27:08,340 --> 00:27:10,360
The duty of the head of the Zhang Family

334
00:27:11,060 --> 00:27:13,470
is to make sure no outsiders

335
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,400
get their hands on the Zanghai Flower.

336
00:27:16,250 --> 00:27:18,750
