343
00:27:32,970 --> 00:27:34,009
But due

344
00:27:34,010 --> 00:27:36,880
to the sudden urgency of the incident

345
00:27:37,410 --> 00:27:40,030
and the major threat he was facing,

346
00:27:40,170 --> 00:27:41,230
he needed

347
00:27:41,620 --> 00:27:44,680
someone else to keep guard
over the field of Zanghai Flower.

348
00:27:48,730 --> 00:27:50,750
My brother seized a tape recorded

349
00:27:50,930 --> 00:27:52,969
by Zhang Qiling

350
