for us and Zhang Qiling.

395
00:30:01,730 --> 00:30:03,080
We never expected

396
00:30:04,100 --> 00:30:06,360
a brat we got to know from our adventure

397
00:30:06,580 --> 00:30:09,400
to overturn the fate
of the Zhang Family.

398
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:13,859
On the second day

399
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:16,120
after Zhang Qiling
joined the Zhang Family Ancient Tower,

400
00:30:16,490 --> 00:30:17,950
our elders told us

401
00:30:18,900 --> 00:30:20,470
that the Zhang Family was gone.

402
00:30:22,730 --> 00:30:24,640
Tianshou illness no longer existed.

403
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:26,470
There was no suffering anymore.

404
00:30:26,970 --> 00:30:28,600
We could leave the place.

405
00:30:30,340 --> 00:30:32,160
Back then, we were too young

406
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:35,360
to understand what it meant.

407
00:30:37,340 --> 00:30:38,880
We only knew

408
00:30:39,820 --> 00:30:41,990
